Package: DLabLinguistics
Title: Analysis of Linguistically Embedded Text Components from the Linguistics Swift Package
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Rodney", "Dyer", , "rodney@dyerlab.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads the SQLite corpus store produced by the Dyerlab Linguistics
    Swift package and provides tools for differential analysis of compositional,
    natural language, and transformer-based embeddings on components of
    scientific research manuscripts. Handles binary Float32 vector
    deserialisation, database connection management, and common operations such
    as cosine similarity and L2 normalisation.
